The results page is divided into a total_number_of_pages
An ordered list of hyperlinked numbers is displayed
The current page number is disabled
If there's only one page
    Don't show the pagination
Else:
    If between the current and the first page are more than 3 pages:
        Hide the numbers 
        If I'm in the first page:
            Show the next two pages
    If between the current and the first or last page are more than 3 pages:
        Hide the numbers
        If I'm in the last page:
            Show the previews two pages
